                "EN": "This is the most talented mechanic in all of Belobog and rock star. Did we mention she's also the sister of Captain Gepard Landau of the Silvermane Guards?<br><br><i>\"Stop. Stop that. Keep the first part, and leave out the second part.\"<br>\"I'd like you not to gloss over my identity like that... I, Serval Landau, am no one's accessory.\"<br><br>\"...Oh, there's nothing else afterward? Okay. Let me chip in then: If something's broken, drop into the Neverwinter Workshop in the Administrative District to see me, any time.\"<br>\"What's that, you wanna hear some rock'n'roll? Well, that's even better — drop into our Neverwinter Workshop in the Administrative District to rock this city — with Mechanical Fever!\"</i>"
